 to give spears a bit of a boost by giving them a +1 damage bonus:

more documentation here:
https://www.gibberlings3.net/forums/topic/36242-expanded-alterclonedelete_effect-functions/

used:

version history:
  12/12/22: initial coding

platform:
  all

*/

